<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #FFA500; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
      .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; }
      .product-info { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #FFA500; }
      .warning { background-color: #FFF3CD; border: 1px solid #FFE69C; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #FFA500; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>‚ö†Ô∏è Maintenance Due Soon</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= @recipient.name %>,</p>
        <p>This is a reminder that maintenance is due soon for the following equipment:</p>
        <div class="product-info">
          <h3><%= @product.name %></h3>
          <p><strong>Barcode:</strong> <%= @product.barcode %></p>
          <p><strong>Maintenance Task:</strong> <%= @schedule.name %></p>
          <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @schedule.description %></p>
          <p><strong>Frequency:</strong> Every <%= @schedule.interval_value %> <%= @schedule.interval_unit %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="warning">
          <strong>‚è∞ Due Date:</strong> <%= @schedule.next_due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %><br/>
          <strong>üìÖ Days Remaining:</strong> <%= @days_until_due %> day(s)
        </div>
        <% if @schedule.last_completed_at %>
          <p><strong>Last Completed:</strong> <%= @schedule.last_completed_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
        <% end %>
        <p>Please schedule this maintenance as soon as possible to prevent equipment downtime.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 30px;"><strong>Note:</strong> If this maintenance is not completed by the due date, the equipment may be automatically blocked from rentals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated notification from your Rentable system.</p>
        <p>¬© <%= Time.current.year %> Rentable. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
